      "trait_type": "Method",
      "value": "Instructions:\nPreheat the Oven:\n\nPreheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).\nAssemble the Mini Bagel Pizzas:\n\nPlace the mini bagel halves on a baking sheet, cut side up.\nSpread a spoonful of pizza sauce on each bagel half.\nSprinkle shredded mozzarella cheese over the sauce.\nAdd mini pepperoni slices and any optional toppings (bell peppers, black olives).\nBake:\n\nBake in the preheated oven for 10-12 minutes, or until the cheese is melted and bubbly.\nServe:\n\nGarnish with fresh basil leaves if desired.\nServe warm.\nLet'a me a'tell you!  Even the keeds love Luigi's a'Famous A'pizz!   You a'gonna have so much fun makin' a'these tiny a'pizz!"
